3fab2dd92ad40a523a44b0a2457f8ce55","tid":401813,"uid":5143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:58:20.000Z","msg":"開過個post得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d843265aebfc99492276cd1307d8abc3ef1d4e11","tid":401813,"uid":1009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:58:20.000Z","msg":"開過個啦好on9呀"},{"pid":"c14f67b9b3b66299673b8807e6f766342786f6a3","tid":401813,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:58:57.000Z","msg":"曾效力阿仙奴的前威爾斯國腳赫臣表示，阿仙奴若果想出戰下屆歐聯，就不要想前四，應學曼聯專心歐霸盃。<br />\n<br />\n赫臣認為阿仙奴今季想取得前4並不容易，所以為了下屆歐聯席位，應從歐霸盃著手。<br />\n<br />\n基奧特解釋留隊原因想喺阿仙奴贏錦標<br />\n<br />\n一直都能保住前四的阿仙奴，上季只得第5，令兵工廠缺席今屆歐聯賽事。<br />\n<br />\n今季阿仙奴開季成績麻麻，但在歐霸分組賽首場就旗開得勝，主場以3：1擊敗科隆 。<br />\n<br />\n前阿仙奴前鋒赫臣表示球隊應面對現實：「前四很難達到，我覺得應該學上季的曼聯，將重心放到歐霸盃，一舉奪盃再取得歐聯入場券。我認為阿仙奴與AC米蘭都是歐霸盃的熱門。」"},{"pid":"df862dcc88dd4052567b166b6390248591c52405","tid":401813,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:59:20.000Z","msg":"成班on9上連登都要咁驚"},{"pid":"3baad3c40ee9b4f8b05d0e4bda70cfa1020dbfb9","tid":401813,"uid":61902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:59:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 串還串 個topic可唔可以唔好咁柒</blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n好撚柒..."},{"pid":"d715e2a8a6471477f45d3181f6b8ef59f3b3eeb8","tid":401813,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:00:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班on9上連登都要咁驚</blockquote><br />\n係你個topic太柒呀<br />\n再串既topic都開過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1e0dc72753e8d4e6dc6fe69ce2005ce3ce5f4b","tid":401813,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:00:15.000Z","msg":"網上唔係你串就人地串架啦,<br />\n少忽肉咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h